title: Custom iron on Jersey Number and name, Personalized jersey name decal, Custom team iron on,  personalized team jersey number
description:
PLEASE SELECT NUMBER AND NAME OPTIONS SEPERATELY

High Quality Iron-On decals for sports suits, and jerseys rugby tshirts.

Easily applicable with domestic iron or heat press. 

:::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::

You can make easily personalized jerseys t-shirts, hoodies, cushion, tote bag, towels, apron etc. for you or your friends.

You can easily customize your Jerseys or other clothes with premium quality iron-on vinyl transfers These can be used on any colour tops or t-shirts, and leave no background at all behind the print. These are a premium vinyl transfer, not to be confused with a regularly printed iron-on transfer. The style of numbers and names are in the type with the famous clubs. You need to select the name size and number size separately. Please select the name and numbers separately and add to the cart. Name and number are generally two separate decals due to shipping size. You can apply them in order. We will send you a detailed instructions paper in the parcel. We can do a custom design for your team if you need. Please contact for team sets.

Our Decals are made up of a high-quality durable grade of Iron-On vinyl that is easily applied to your fabrics by your iron. 

These decals can be applied to 100% Cotton, 100% Uncoated Polyester and Cotton/Polyester blends.

Not recommended for use on Nylon, or 100% polyester as the fabric can melt under the iron at high temperatures.

description:
★All orders are processed within 1-3 business days.
★We can adjust sizing needs to most of our decals by request. Decals under 6" wide is not an option.
★Message response time is 24-48 hours (usually within 24 hours).
★For customization requests on designs, please message us BEFORE you place an order.
★We only communicate through Etsy messages.  If we have a question and there is no response, your order will be canceled and refunded on the day it's due to ship.
★The vinyl will not stick to orange-peel or similar heavily textured and bumpy surface. Low-VOC or Zero-VOC "green friendly" paints are problematic and the vinyl does not adhere well. ORACAL (the vinyl we use)  recommends applying to smooth, semi-gloss or gloss enamel paint. If possible, avoid matte finish Latex paints and paints that contain anti-graffiti agents or stain blockers. See our FAQ's about vinyl for more information.

"This is Us" Lettering Vinyl Decal Wall Art Decor 

Choose your size and color in the drop down boxes. The color chart is in the pictures. If you don't see a size option that fits your needs, message me! It's no problem to make custom sizes. 

Extra Extra Small
8 inches wide by 2.31 inches tall

24 inches wide by 6.94 inches tall

32 inches wide by 9.25 inches tall

42 inches wide by 12.14 inches tall 

Extra Extra Large
52 inches wide by 15.03 inches tall 


Photos are illustrations and are not sized to any scale.

+++++++
What You'll Receive:

- The decal in between the backing paper and already applied transfer tape
- Instructions on how to place your decal

The matte vinyl I stock is high quality oracal 631. It is removable. Not reusable. It has a matte finish, meaning it is not shiny. It has the appearance and texture of regular printer paper - but thicker. It has a thickness of 3 mil. It has an outdoor durability of 3 years. Matte will have a painted-on look and blends well into painted surfaces. Extra low and especially zero VOC paints (environmentally friendly) can be problematic. It is recommended that decals are not applied to new paint and to wait about 3 weeks. Decals may leave a slight residue after removal. If the paint is old, some slight damage could occur upon removal.

***I advise against applying decals onto orange-peel textured walls, or anything similar that doesn't offer enough flat surface area for a decal to stick onto. If you are unsure whether your decal will stick, send me a detailed photo of the surface. Please see the FAQ's at the bottom of this page for more information.

Photos are illustrations and are not sized to scale. Photos depicting props, furniture, lighting, etc. will not be included with the vinyl decal.

description:

_______

⭐️ EASY LICENSING :)

Personal & Commercial Use are allowed for:
✅ unlimited projects & unlimited sales for finished physical items and finished (uneditable) digital items
✅ use on your own website
✅ you do not have to provide font credit

Absolutely NO:
❌ reselling, redistributing, offering for free, tracing, or altering the fonts from their original form, selling of embroidery fonts, or selling of the individual characters in alternate file formats
❌ claiming as your own creation

Additional licensing required for:
⚠️ server installation
⚠️ embedding in a .pdf for use with apps like Templett or Corjl
⚠️ app usage

✉️ Send me an Etsy message for information on additional licensing.

⭐️ HELPFUL LINKS

If you have questions about how to do certain things prior to purchase, I recommend the following reading material.

📌 Installing fonts on a computer: https://beckmccormick.com/installing-fonts/
📌 Installing fonts on an iPad or iPhone: https://beckmccormick.com/how-to-download-fonts-on-ipad-iphone-installing-custom-fonts/
📌 Installing fonts to use with Procreate: https://beckmccormick.com/how-to-install-custom-procreate-fonts-on-your-ipad/
📌 Installing fonts to use with Canva: https://beckmccormick.com/upload-custom-fonts-to-canva/
📌 Accessing the special decorative characters: https://beckmccormick.com/accessing-opentype-features/
📌 Accessing the special decorative characters in Design Space: https://beckmccormick.com/how-to-add-flourishes-to-fonts-in-cricut-design-space/
_______

Read on to learn more about what makes my handlettered fonts so special! 
 
HANDLETTERED FONTS FOR GRAPHIC DESIGNERS, AGENCIES, AND THE CRAFTY CRICUT FAN

Whatcha gonna do with all those fonts?

There is no limit to the number of projects you can create using one, some, or all of these lovely handlettered fonts. The most popular uses that my customers tell me about are creating logos & branded materials for their clients or creating gifts like artwork & quotes, t shirts, coffee mugs, farmhouse signs, or other products. You may even use the fonts to create + sell your own SVG files or printables if you're considering starting up your own small business.

This font collection is versatile, and includes a wide variety of cursive fonts. You can find calligraphy fonts, signature fonts, farmhouse fonts, rustic fonts, and fonts that mimic handwriting. In addition to that, you'll also find some whimsical handlettered sans fonts and handwritten serif fonts.

Fonts are super easy to install, and may be used in any program that accesses your system's installed fonts -- that includes things like Word or Pages, Excel or Numbers, Photoshop, Illustrator, or other Adobe programs, and more. You may also upload to your own personal Canva account, or import to Procreate so that you can create designs there, as well.
 
CAN I USE FONT BUNDLES FOR CRICUT DESIGN SPACE OR SILHOUETTE STUDIO?

Yes! I get this question all the time -- you most definitely can use these fonts in Cricut Design Space. This is one of the most popular font bundles for cutting machine users - it's very easy to use with your Cricut Machine. All you need to do, once the fonts are downloaded, is install the fonts on your computer! Make sure you restart Design Space, and the fonts will show up in the System Fonts section when your text tool is selected. Make your text box, and begin typing!

You can follow similar steps for your Silhouette machine software - simply install, restart, select your text tool, & type!

I have helpful blog post tutorials available, just in case you need a little extra helping hand. I gotchu.
 
SAY NO TO FREE FONTS FOR CRICUT

Stop trying to find free fonts to use with Design Space - free fonts might sound cool, but you'll soon realize you're working with humdrum, boring fonts with limited features. Some of those fonts are a hot mess, let's be honest.

My handlettered fonts are feature-rich, full of so many extra glyphs, swashes, hearts, alternate characters, and more! They're also PUA encoded, so that makes finding the special characters a total breeze - just use FontBook or Character Map if you're not working with OpenType-friendly software. (Please feel free to message me about this - I have a super handy blog post so you can learn!) You do not need Cricut Access to use these fonts within Design Space.

You're probably wondering if you can use these fonts commercially, too! The short answer is YES! I like to keep my licenses as simple as possible. If you scroll back up to the top, you can see my easy, up front licensing. You'll make your money back in no time at all.
 
WHAT'S STOPPING YOU

Seriously, $29 gets you access to over 200 fonts, worth over $2400, AND it includes commercial use. Totally unheard of, it's a steal of a deal. I love what I do, and letters are my thing. If crafting is your thing, designing SVG files & cut files is your jam, logo designs are what you love, or any other type of design work...this collection is for you. 

There are so many projects just waiting to be created - thousands of Etsy customers & other Etsy sellers can't be wrong with glowing five-star reviews. Go take a look yourself! Not sure if I'm legit? Find me on my own website, Creative Market, Creative Fabrica, FontBundles.net, and other design resource marketplaces. My fonts are used by Amazon, Minted, Smallwoods, Smucker's & more - it's very humbling and SUPER exciting. Letters feed my family, and I would be so thrilled see my fonts as a powerful addition to your font arsenal, helping you do the things that you love, too!

PS, I offer lovingly handlettered SVG files, as well. These cut files are top notch, fantastic quality, and ready to upload as-is to your design software. Use a cutting machine to create your own project, or upload to a printer of your choice to have your apparel or decor made for you - easy peasy.

Questions? Shoot me a message, I'd love to hear from you & make sure you have exactly the information you need!
